1.16
log
@From Areca, this also fully supports ARC-1264, ARC-1284 and the upcoming
ARC-1883
@
text
@.\"	$OpenBSD: arc.4,v 1.15 2014/01/24 00:24:41 chris Exp $
.\"
.\" Copyright (c) 2006 David Gwynne <dlg@@openbsd.org>
.\"
